RT: ## RT           : Mean retention time (peak apex) of the reference peak in seconds
## MZ           : Mean mass-to-charge ratio of the reference peak
## LeftRTBorder : Retention time of the start of the reference peak in seconds
## RightRTBorder: Retention time of the end of the reference peak in seconds
## MZDeviation  : Deviation of the reference peak in ppm (approximately 6 * standard deviation of the profile mode peak)
